<div id="section">
<font color="black">
<p><u><b><center> Installation</center></b></u></p>

<p>1. Click <a src="http://spring.io/tools/sts\">here</a> to go to the website.</p>

<img src="http://i304.photobucket.com/albums/nn197/nrotondaro/pic64_zpssiyeqdmm.png" alt="Image" style="width:700px;height:381px;"/>

<p> 2. Once downloaded, right click the file and select 'extract all'. Make sure the folder is accessible and then click extract.</p>

<img src="http://i304.photobucket.com/albums/nn197/nrotondaro/pic67_zps50c6zocc.png" alt="Image" style="width:700px;height:383px;" />

<p> 3. Once the file is open, click 'sts-bundle'. After that, you will click &lsquo;sts-3.7.0.RELEASE'.</p>

<img src="http://i304.photobucket.com/albums/nn197/nrotondaro/pic65_zpsi6jfhsgj.png" alt="Image" style="width:700px;height:384px;" />

<img src="http://i304.photobucket.com/albums/nn197/nrotondaro/pic66_zps3yggrvpj.png" alt="Image" style="width:700px;height:384px;" />

<p2> 4. Then click STS (the application not the configuration settings) to start up the application. </p>

<img src="http://i304.photobucket.com/albums/nn197/nrotondaro/pic68_zpsn8o52cru.png" alt="Image" style="width:700px;height:384;" />

